#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "Namestitev"

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to obtain &kxstitch;"
msgstr "Kako pridobiti &kxstitch;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kxstitch; source can be found at <ulink url=\"http://download.kde.org/"
"stable/kxstitch/\">http://download.kde.org/stable/kxstitch/</ulink>. The "
"&kxstitch; homepage can be found at <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/"
"KXStitch\">http://userbase.kde.org/KXStitch</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"&kxstitch; vir lahko najdete na <ulink url=\"http://download.kde.org/stable/"
"kxstitch/\">http://download.kde.org/stable/kxstitch/</ulink>. &kxstitch; "
"domačo stran lahko najdete na <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/KXStitch"
"\">http://userbase.kde.org/KXStitch</ulink>"

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Zahteve"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kxstitch; has been written with &Qt; 5.x and &kf5-full;."
msgstr "&kxstitch; je bilo napisano z &Qt; 5.x in &kf5-full;."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the image import functions the ImageMagick libraries are required, this "
"includes the development headers ImageMagick and Magick++, these are "
"available with your distribution or from <ulink url=\"http://www.imagemagick."
"org/\">http://www.imagemagick.org/</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za funkcije uvoza slik so potrebne knjižnice ImageMagick, to vključuje "
"razvojni glavi ImageMagick in Magick++, ki sta na voljo pri vaši "
"distribuciji ali na <ulink url=\"http://www.imagemagick.org/\">http://www ."
"imagemagick.org/</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compilation and Installation"
msgstr "Prevajanje in namestitev"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compilation of KXStitch requires cmake and suitable build tools, make, gcc, "
"etc. A build script has been provided which should perform the necessary "
"compilation operations and install KXStitch for which you may be required to "
"enter the root password."
msgstr ""
"Prevajanje KXStitch zahteva cmake in ustrezna orodja za gradnjo, make, gcc "
"itd. Zagotovljen je bil skript za gradnjo, ki bi moral izvesti potrebne "
"operacije prevajanja in namestiti KXStitch, za katerega boste morda morali "
"vnesti geslo root."

#. Tag: screen
#: install.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>bash$</prompt><command>./build.sh</command>"
msgstr "<prompt>bash$</prompt><command>./build.sh</command>"
